Subset the provided datamart data to just the latest snapshot per model.

latestSnapshotsOnly.Rd

If there is just one snapshot, nothing will change. It works for both model and predictor tables. If there is no snapshottime field, it will not do anything.

latestSnapshotsOnly(dt)

Arguments

dt

The data.table with the datamart data.

Value

A data.table with just the latest snapshots per model.

Examples

latestSnapshotsOnly(admdatamart_binning)
